examples.en: Every wood is usable for some good purpose.
Is any of this junk usable?
2000 square feet of usable office space

The vase has a few fine cracks, but it is still usable.
Although the spade is usable as a snow shovel, it doesn't do a very good job.

The computer language involved was readily usable.
